{"id":563144,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/07/新华网-湖南宁乡县遭遇特大严重洪涝灾害/","date":"2017-07-07T04:24:04Z","modified":"2017-07-07T07:39:58Z","title":"新华网 | 湖南宁乡县遭遇特大严重洪涝灾害","content":"<p>新华社长沙7月7日电 记者7日从湖南省宁乡县举行的2017年防汛抢险救灾情况通报会上获悉，据初步统计，全县受灾人口81．5万，占全县人口的56％，全县派出12个救灾核查组，累计核实因灾死亡、意外落水溺亡、失联人员共44人。</p>\n<p>6月22日以来，宁乡发生了历年同期历时最长、范围最广、雨量最多、强度最大的强降雨，遭遇了宁乡有水文、气象记录60年以来最为严重的自然灾害。</p>\n<p>另附宁乡县防汛抗灾情况通报文件</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/62ac1493gy1fhb4utm3f0j21kw23uk1x.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-563149\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/62ac1493gy1fhb4utm3f0j21kw23uk1x.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"587\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/62ac1493gy1fhb4utm3f0j21kw23uk1x.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/62ac1493gy1fhb4utm3f0j21kw23uk1x-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/62ac1493gy1fhb4ur2ti2j21kw23uamh.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-563148\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/62ac1493gy1fhb4ur2ti2j21kw23uamh.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"587\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/62ac1493gy1fhb4ur2ti2j21kw23uamh.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/62ac1493gy1fhb4ur2ti2j21kw23uamh-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/62ac1493gy1fhb4un64o3j21kw23ugwz.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-563146\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/62ac1493gy1fhb4un64o3j21kw23ugwz.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"587\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/62ac1493gy1fhb4un64o3j21kw23ugwz.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/07/62ac1493gy1fhb4un64o3j21kw23ugwz-225x300.jpg 225w\